  //   Falls back to CPU gracefully when no GPU is available.
  // ContextSize (default 8192): context window in tokens.
  // KeepLoaded (default true): models stay resident after first use.
  //   Set false to auto-unload after IdleCooldownMinutes of inactivity.
  // IdleCooldownMinutes (default 5): idle time before unloading an
